1
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:26,799
Your Majesty.

2
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:28,159
An urgent dispatch.

3
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,599
A great victory at the front.

4
00:01:29,959 --> 00:01:32,599
Ning Chen led troops to strike the Northern Royal Court.

5
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,000
He captured Zuoting Wang alive.

6
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,239
And took three thousand prisoners.

7
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,680
While passing through Lingzhou,

8
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,359
he also discovered a gold mine.

9
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:40,680
Liang Jingwu, defender of Beilin Pass,

10
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:44,040
crushed forty thousand Tuoluo troops head-on.

11
00:01:45,599 --> 00:01:47,280
This Zuoting Wang

12
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,599
is truly worthless.

13
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,560
Truly worthy of Our esteem.

14
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:52,959
A young prodigy indeed.

15
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,439
This lad never fails to surprise Us.

16
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,480
First a gold mine,

17
00:01:58,599 --> 00:02:00,280
then capturing Zuoting Wang alive.

18
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,519
Such a magnificent feat,

19
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,400
in all of Our Great Xuan,

20
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,200
no one has ever achieved before.

21
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:06,280
Ning Chen's deeds shake the past and dazzle the present.

22
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,680
Standing supreme above all,

23
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,039
handling great burdens with ease,

24
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,520
free and unrestrained.

25
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:14,280
Then We shall grant him the title of Marquis Xiaoyao.

26
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,719
What say you, Our beloved ministers?

27
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:20,879
Granting him a marquisate?

28
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:21,919
Royal Father,

29
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:23,360
since Your Majesty ascended the throne,

30
00:02:23,719 --> 00:02:24,879
no marquis has ever been appointed.

31
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:27,599
Though Ning Chen has rendered military service,

32
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:29,240
to grant him a marquisate now

33
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:33,319
would place him on par with this Chancellor.

34
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,719
Your Majesty,

35
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:37,639
this old subject deems it improper.

36
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,439
Ning Chen has merely won a single battle.

37
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:41,599
If he is granted a marquisate for that,

38
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:44,840
how could the seasoned generals of Great Xuan,

39
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,759
with their countless feats, ever accept it?

40
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:49,560
Lord Yu,

41
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:50,840
in letters,

42
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,759
Ning Chen's poetry stands unrivaled in all the realm.

43
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:54,960
In arms,

44
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,039
Ning Chen marched a thousand miles

45
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,360
and captured Zuoting Wang alive.

46
00:02:58,719 --> 00:02:59,599
And what of you?

47
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,800
In this old subject's view,

48
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,000
Ning Chen's merits

49
00:03:02,199 --> 00:03:04,319
fully warrant the title of Marquis Xiaoyao.

50
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:09,879
Your Majesty, I beg to report.

51
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:13,199
This subject also finds it improper.

52
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:16,919
Ning Ziming,

53
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:18,000
have you lost your mind?

54
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:19,719
Ning Chen is your own son.

55
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,360
At court, there are no fathers and sons,

56
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,120
only subjects of His Majesty.

57
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,240
You...

58
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,520
Royal Father,

59
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:30,800
this son also believes

60
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,560
that to grant Ning Chen a marquisate now

61
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,479
is truly improper.

62
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,080
Ning Chen has indeed rendered great service,

63
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:39,080
but he is not yet of age to be made a general and marquis.

64
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:39,960
This...

65
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,240
A pack of scoundrels.

66
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,719
Especially the Crown Prince,

67
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:47,680
that idiot.

68
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:49,520
It is one thing for others to obstruct this,

69
00:03:49,639 --> 00:03:50,960
but why must you jump in as well?

70
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,639
We have groomed Ning Chen with such care

71
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,080
all for your sake.

72
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:58,840
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

73
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:01,280
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

74
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:23,160
As for the marquisate,

75
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:26,319
since all Our ministers oppose it,

76
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,199
so be it.

77
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,480
We shall discuss it another day.

78
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,839
Then We shall await Ning Chen's return to the capital.

79
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,560
All ministers shall accompany Us beyond the city walls

80
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,399
to welcome Ning Chen's triumphant return.

81
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,639
Very well.

82
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,959
Greetings, Your Majesty.

83
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:16,680
Rise.

84
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

85
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,920
You have grown thinner again.

86
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,000
It seems at the frontier,

87
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,800
you have endured great hardship.

88
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,920
To ease Your Majesty's burdens

89
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,439
is this subject's bounden duty.

90
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,759
The true hardship was borne by the soldiers.

91
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,199
A thousand-li rapid march,

92
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,639
capturing Zuoting Wang alive.

93
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,360
Enduring the elements all along the way,

94
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,399
and eating snow to stave off hunger.

95
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,680
Fortunately, we did not fail our mission,

96
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:41,240
nor betray Your Majesty's grace.

97
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,360
You need not seek merit on their behalf.

98
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,120
Their meritorious deeds,

99
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,759
We have kept them all in Our heart.

100
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,480
Not one shall be overlooked.

101
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:52,519
Your Majesty,

102
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:55,480
this subject has one more matter to report.

103
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:58,439
Granted.

104
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:01,000
Bring him forth.

105
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,680
Zhang Yuancang, Prefect of Lingzhou,

106
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:16,519
illegally mined gold,

107
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,160
and brought ruin upon the region.

108
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:20,639
Kong Yongchun, Military Inspector of Beilin Pass,

109
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,639
committed treason,

110
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,439
colluded with Zuoting Wang,

111
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,360
and caused the deaths of six generals of Great Xuan,

112
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,279
along with tens of thousands of soldiers.

113
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:31,040
Their crimes are unforgivable.

114
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,680
How dare you, Ning Chen!

115
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:37,040
Was Zhang Yuancang of Lingzhou

116
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,959
not already beheaded for public display?

117
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,399
How dare you deceive His Majesty!

118
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:44,639
Your Majesty,

119
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:47,160
deceiving the throne is a capital offense.

120
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,399
However, this time Ning Chen

121
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,639
has rendered great service to our dynasty,

122
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:53,000
and is gifted in both letters and arms.

123
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,560
In this subject's view,

124
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,160
his merits offset his faults.

125
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,279
It is best to give him a chance to prove himself.

126
00:06:59,199 --> 00:06:59,639
Your Majesty,

127
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,079
the situation was dire,

128
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,360
and this subject had no choice but to do so.

129
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:07,519
Zhang Yuancang was not the mastermind.

130
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,240
Behind him

131
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:12,399
stands a person of great power and rank.

132
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:22,800
This subject was about to depart for the frontier,

133
00:07:23,319 --> 00:07:24,279
and feared that Zhang Yuancang

134
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,079
would be silenced by the one behind it all.

135
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,000
So this subject had no choice but to deceive everyone.

136
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,439
Furthermore,

137
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:31,959
Kong Yongchun, a mere military inspector,

138
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,959
could never have had the audacity

139
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,360
to commit such treason on his own.

140
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,560
Someone instructed him as well.

141
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,000
Then have you discovered

142
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:41,399
who this mastermind is?

143
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:42,879
Your Majesty,

144
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,199
much of the evidence is still in the city.

145
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,879
Please return to the palace and wait, Your Majesty.

146
00:07:48,639 --> 00:07:50,879
This subject shall return shortly.

147
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,079
Very well.

148
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,439
You shall all return to the palace with Us and wait.

149
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,879
No one is permitted to leave.

150
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,160
We obey Your Majesty's decree.

151
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:04,160
Ning Chen,

152
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,639
do be careful.

153
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,560
He is indeed an illegitimate son.

154
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,040
Yes.

155
00:08:29,079 --> 00:08:29,759
Ning Yinyi.

156
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:31,839
Ning Yinyi! Ning Yinyi!

157
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:33,559
Ning Yinyi!

158
00:08:34,279 --> 00:08:36,120
Not bad, you've become a boss now.

159
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,759
Xinghe, you're getting more handsome by the day.

160
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:38,679
Your skin is fairer too.

161
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,600
Got a beauty treatment?

162
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,360
Have you ever seen such a handsome boss?

163
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,600
Of course not.

164
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:44,559
Wuxian,

165
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,279
you are getting stronger and stronger.

166
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,480
Still working out every day, I take it?

167
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,840
Mainly because nutrition is better now.

168
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:50,200
Ning Yinyi,

169
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,360
we have, with our own hands,

170
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,200
realized our dream.

171
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,720
A bun shop!

172
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:56,679
By the way,

173
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,679
today happens to be our opening day,

174
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,960
and you brothers happened to pass by.

175
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,240
Come.

176
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:00,960
Have a taste, try one, try one.

177
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:01,440
Try one, have a taste.

178
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,039
Come, come, come.

179
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:02,639
Here.

180
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:03,759
Take it, take it, everyone have a taste.

181
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:05,960
Good, have a taste.

182
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:06,759
This very shop here,

183
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,440
come and support us!

184
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:07,960
Have a taste.

185
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,759
Brothers, eat up!

186
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,840
There's more if that's not enough.

187
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:11,960
Come by often when you have time.

188
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:12,840
Ning Yinyi,

189
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,720
give our bun shop

190
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,240
a name, will you?

191
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,200
Yes, yes, yes.

192
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:19,519
Goubuli! Open more branches!

193
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,039
Grow bigger and stronger.

194
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:23,960
May your kind words come true.

195
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,679
Bigger and stronger!

196
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:28,080
I have a daughter just coming of age.

197
00:09:28,399 --> 00:09:29,679
Come over to my house for a meal.

198
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:32,480
My dear Ning!

199
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:36,159
My dear Ning!

200
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:36,879
Lord Ning!

201
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:39,480
Wait for me!

202
00:09:50,399 --> 00:09:50,879
Excellent.

203
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,519
Old Gao, Old Feng.

204
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,320
Go to the Liu Family Cloth Shop in the West Market.

205
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:53,919
Search for the secret letters.

206
00:09:54,039 --> 00:09:54,720
We shall split up.

207
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:55,440
Yes, yes.

208
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:59,039
Master Ning saw me.

209
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,399
Master Pan saw me too.

210
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:03,159
It seems Lord Ning truly cares for you, miss.

211
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,039
Once he is done with his duties,

212
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:05,320
he will surely come for you.

213
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,480
Wonderful.

214
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,240
Steward Ding.

215
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,480
Has the Chancellor returned?

216
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:14,080
No.

217
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,480
That bastard Ning Chen.

218
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:20,000
He actually captured Zuoting Wang.

219
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,799
Seize him at once.

220
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:40,799
What are you doing?

221
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,360
What is this?

222
00:10:42,519 --> 00:10:43,639
This is the Chancellor's residence.

223
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:46,879
Trespass here is punishable by death. Do you know that?

224
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:52,039
Death!

225
00:10:53,279 --> 00:10:55,480
Do you know Kong Yongchun, Inspector of Beilin Pass?

226
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,159
I do not.

227
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:59,519
I have no idea what you are talking about.

228
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:02,879
Take him away.

229
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,200
Move.

230
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:08,799
That, um...

231
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,159
Chen'er, about that...

232
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,080
That, um...

233
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,639
The secret letters Kong Yongchun hid,

234
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,200
we have found them.

235
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:13,759
Yes.

236
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:16,600
This time,

237
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,320
I shall bring down the Left Chancellor.

238
00:11:30,399 --> 00:11:31,960
This subject greets Your Majesty.

239
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:33,559
Rise.

240
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:34,919
Thank you, Your Majesty.

241
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:38,159
Ning Chen.

242
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,600
Have you found the evidence?

243
00:11:41,519 --> 00:11:42,000
Yes.

244
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,679
Then you may now tell Us,

245
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:47,720
who this traitor is.

246
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:48,840
Your Majesty,

247
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:50,559
Illegally mining gold,

248
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,120
colluding with the enemy and committing treason,

249
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:53,799
slaughtering the innocent,

250
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,399
persecuting loyal officials.

251
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,159
The greatest vermin of Our Great Xuan

252
00:11:58,919 --> 00:11:59,879
is the Left Chancellor.

253
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:09,639
This old subject has served for decades,

254
00:12:10,279 --> 00:12:11,799
diligently

255
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,360
and conscientiously,

256
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:15,960
graced by Your Majesty's heavenly favor,

257
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,159
trusted with Your Majesty's esteem.

258
00:12:19,039 --> 00:12:19,720
What more

259
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:22,759
could this old subject possibly want?

260
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,159
How dare you, Ning Chen!

261
00:12:26,679 --> 00:12:29,159
Spouting nonsense before His Majesty!

262
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:30,759
Your Majesty,

263
00:12:31,159 --> 00:12:32,600
the Left Chancellor serves the Son of Heaven.

264
00:12:32,799 --> 00:12:34,840
He has no reason whatsoever to commit treason.

265
00:12:37,759 --> 00:12:38,720
I beg Your Majesty's permission

266
00:12:39,559 --> 00:12:42,120
to summon Kong Yongchun and Zhang Yuancang.

267
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:43,879
Granted.

268
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:47,679
Kneel.

269
00:12:52,519 --> 00:12:53,360
Before His Majesty,

270
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,279
confess the truth at once.

271
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:57,639
Your Majesty,

272
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:00,879
this guilty subject is Zhang Yuancang, former Prefect of Lingzhou,

273
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,600
a disciple of the Left Chancellor.

274
00:13:03,399 --> 00:13:04,840
By the Left Chancellor's orders,

275
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,039
I secretly mined gold.

276
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:11,919
This guilty subject is Kong Yongchun, Inspector of Beilin Pass,

277
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,720
a disciple of the Left Chancellor.

278
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:16,240
For years, under the Left Chancellor's orders,

279
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:18,200
I secretly monitored Beilin Pass,

280
00:13:18,759 --> 00:13:20,240
colluded with Zuoting Wang,

281
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:24,080
and conspired to murder six generals of Great Xuan,

282
00:13:24,399 --> 00:13:25,840
along with tens of thousands of soldiers.

283
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:28,879
This subject is guilty!

284
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,639
What?

285
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,279
Reporting to Your Majesty,

286
00:13:35,759 --> 00:13:36,919
Kong Yongchun has confessed.

287
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,879
The secret letters proving his collusion with the Left Chancellor

288
00:13:39,799 --> 00:13:41,039
have just been seized by this subject.

289
00:14:01,559 --> 00:14:02,399
Left Chancellor.

290
00:14:03,279 --> 00:14:04,519
Speak to Us.

291
00:14:05,279 --> 00:14:06,600
Why would you commit

292
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,960
such a heinous act of treason?

293
00:14:10,159 --> 00:14:11,039
Your Majesty, I beg for your clear judgment.

294
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:14,080
This old subject is truly innocent!

295
00:14:14,639 --> 00:14:16,919
Your Majesty is familiar with this old subject's handwriting.

296
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:20,120
I beg Your Majesty to discern the truth.

297
00:14:22,759 --> 00:14:24,000
You have served as an official for decades.

298
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,919
If you did not always cover your tracks,

299
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,120
how could you possibly

300
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,559
have risen to head all the officials?

301
00:14:28,879 --> 00:14:29,639
A matter such as this

302
00:14:30,679 --> 00:14:33,039
would naturally not be written by your own hand, Lord Chancellor.

303
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,080
Your Majesty.

304
00:14:35,679 --> 00:14:36,519
Upon this subject's investigation,

305
00:14:37,159 --> 00:14:37,879
those secret letters,

306
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:40,320
half were written by the Left Chancellor's steward,

307
00:14:41,279 --> 00:14:41,759
and the other half,

308
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:44,720
by his confidant, Ma Kaicheng.

309
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,519
Where are those two curs?

310
00:14:46,879 --> 00:14:47,480
Your Majesty,

311
00:14:48,279 --> 00:14:50,399
the Left Chancellor's steward awaits outside the hall.

312
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,039
Summon him.

313
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,159
The Left Chancellor's secret letters,

314
00:15:09,919 --> 00:15:11,480
were they ghostwritten by you?

315
00:15:12,799 --> 00:15:13,279
Your Majesty,

316
00:15:13,919 --> 00:15:14,960
this humble commoner is innocent!

317
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,919
This commoner has never written any secret letters.

318
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,000
Your Majesty may compare his handwriting,

319
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,200
and the truth will be plain to see.

320
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,039
My lord,

321
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,679
this servant has failed you.

322
00:15:28,879 --> 00:15:29,919
I have betrayed your trust.

323
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:32,200
I cultivated you all these years for nothing,

324
00:15:32,799 --> 00:15:34,559
and looked after your entire family.

325
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,440
Is this how you repay me?

326
00:15:41,559 --> 00:15:42,159
My lord,

327
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:43,639
those secret letters

328
00:15:44,159 --> 00:15:45,759
were indeed written by this servant.

329
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,720
It was I, together with Ma Kaicheng,

330
00:15:48,039 --> 00:15:50,519
who conspired with Kong Yongchun and Zhang Yuancang to plunder the gold mines,

331
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:53,480
causing the deaths of soldiers and generals at the border.

332
00:15:54,639 --> 00:15:55,679
This has nothing to do with my lord.

333
00:15:56,639 --> 00:15:57,879
You wretched scoundrel!

334
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:58,919
How dare you!

335
00:15:59,080 --> 00:15:59,559
Your Majesty,

336
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:03,360
this was all done by myself and Ma Kaicheng.

337
00:16:03,519 --> 00:16:04,600
My lord knew nothing of it.

338
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,519
I beseech Your Majesty to see the truth.

339
00:16:09,759 --> 00:16:11,120
What a loyal dog you are.

340
00:16:11,879 --> 00:16:12,879
A crime of such magnitude,

341
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,840
can a lowly steward like you

342
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:15,679
truly bear it alone?

343
00:16:16,159 --> 00:16:16,679
Ning Chen,

344
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,840
have you never heard the saying,

345
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:22,639
"A chancellor's gatekeeper holds the third rank"?

346
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:26,679
"A chancellor's gatekeeper holds the third rank," indeed.

347
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:28,559
Then I shall see

348
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,720
if the Inspectorate can pry your mouth open.

349
00:16:36,919 --> 00:16:38,080
Do you truly think

350
00:16:38,759 --> 00:16:40,639
I would give you the chance?

351
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,440
What has happened?

352
00:17:02,039 --> 00:17:02,600
Reporting to Your Majesty,

353
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:03,720
the man is dead.

354
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,400
Carry him away.
